Others: The match between Pakistan and England will be played on Saturday, November 11, 2023.
The game will be played at the M. Chinnaswamy Stadium in Bengaluru.
The match is scheduled to start at 10:30 IST (+5:30 GMT).
Star Sports Network has acquired the rights to broadcast the ICC ODI World Cup 2023.
The Pakistan vs England match will be broadcasted live in multiple languages across the Star Sports Network.
The live streaming of the game will be on Disney+ Hotstar.
All the mobile users would be able to view the World Cup clash involving the hosts for free of cost on the Disney+ Hotstar mobile app.
